      <talk_answer link_index="n124_guard_sam-2-d" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ancient Temple Excavation Site... Alright.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Guard Sam$<BR>According to Guard Dickinson at Wind Forest, <FONT color=#a82424>Red Harpy</FONT> flew towards the direction of <FONT color=#a82424>Ancient Temple Excavation Site</FONT>. Rose was abducted not too long ago, so I'm sure you can rescue Rose if you chase after them now!</html>]]></talk_question>
